title: APPROVE OR DENY DAISY CHAIN SANCTUARY?
body:
DAISY CHAIN SANCTUARY PROPOSAL
MDSP-3 (MEOWDAO SHELTER PROPOSAL) - # : 
DAISY CHAIN SANCTUARY MDSP-3
{Summary/ Plan A}

This proposal moves to add Daisy Chain Sanctuary to the list of organizations to donate to for MeowDao. Daisy Chain needs help raising funds and acquiring land and vehicles and tools for their animal Sanctuary. For more information about the organization, go to DaisyChainSanctuary.org 

I have been working with Susan on Daisy Chain for 3 years and she has a grand vision for the organization that not only will assist many felines and horses, though many other animals and environmental issues as well.   Currently we are expanding our Horizons to the crypto realm and will be making NFT's that help fund us and run campaigns to donate to us through meow Dao. Our energy from Meow will go to great purpose in Daisy Chain's hands!  Teaching foster children, their families and veterans compassion through healing and working with animals and humans on various tasks. The act of healing animals can heal people too.
